<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="16Apr1930"><font color="red">16 April 1930</font> <i>Letters III</i> (from Lucia Joyce to Adrienne Monnier): (in French) &hellip; telephone Mr Paul L&eacute;on Littr&eacute; 88-89 if it is still possible to change the word &ldquo;ships&rdquo; to &ldquo;skivs&rdquo; in the phrase &ldquo;seamen. We segn your ships and wives.&rdquo; &hellip; [Giorgio] should lend to Mr L&eacute;on the little black notebook containing all that has been published up to now of W. in P. which is in the cupboard beside his desk </div>
